This directory vendors prebuilt `sqlite-vec` loadable binaries from
https://github.com/asg017/sqlite-vec (Apache License 2.0).

Upstream release: v0.1.9
Upstream license: Apache-2.0

We embed these binaries into pbrainctl at build time and extract them
to a temp file at process startup to preserve single-binary
distribution. See vec.go for the loading mechanism.

To update: download the new release's loadable artifact for each
platform from the upstream releases page and replace the dylib files
in this directory. The filename convention is
sqlite-vec-<GOOS>-<GOARCH>.<ext>.
